title: Panel of presiding officers announced for 298th Senate session
content:
ISLAMABAD, May 12 (APP):Chairman Senate Muhammad Sadiq Sanjrani on Tuesday announced the panel of Presiding officers to act in absence of both the Chairman and Deputy Chairman.
The Chairman chaired the proceedings of 298th Senate session, commenced on the very day.
The panel of Presiding officers comprises Dilawar Khan, Muhammad Akram and Neghat Mirza.
